songs.title: Meet Me in Space
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Woah-oh-oh-oh
Woah-oh-oh-oh

[Verse 1]
Sometimes, I feel I'm growing up
And somehow, the magic's turn to dust
And I don't, no I don't like it
And I'll die, I'll die trying to fight it

[Chorus]
Woah-oh-oh-oh
I'll die trying to fight it
Woah-oh-oh-oh

[Verse 2]
When we were young and out of tune
We screamed, the battle cry o' youth
And I'm sick, I'm so sick of trying
To live forever, when we're all dying

[Breakdown]
(Woah-oh-oh-oh)
Don't take away, my magic insane
Meet me in space, it's beautiful
(Woah-oh-oh-oh)
Inside my brain, my magic insane
Meet me in space, it's beautiful
(Woah-oh-oh-oh)

Meet me in space, it's beautiful
(Woah-oh-oh-oh)
Inside my brain, my magic insane
Meet me in space, it's beautiful

[Bridge]
I wanna love like I've never had my heart broke before
Young and reckless
Young and reckless
I wanna love like I've never had my heart broke before
Young and reckless
Young and reckless
